### More filters
GET http://127.0.0.1:9200/movies/_search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": {
        "bool": {
            "must": { "match": {"genre": "Sci-Fi"} },
            "must_not": { "match": {"title": "trek"} },
            "filter": { "range": { "year": { "gte": "2010", "lt": "2015" }} }
        }
    }
}

