### Partial Matching / Prefix Queries
GET http://127.0.0.1:9200/movies/_search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": {
        "prefix": {
            // year must be text field
            "year": "201"
        }
    }
}

### Partial Matching / Wildcard
GET http://127.0.0.1:9200/movies/_search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": {
        "wildcard": {
            // year must be text field
            "year": "*5*" // 201*, *1*
        }
    }
}


### Search as you type
GET http://127.0.0.1:9200/movies/_search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": {
        "match_phrase_prefix": {
            "title": {
                "query": "star tr",
                "slop": 10
            }
        }
    }
}